{"type": "article", "id": 10444, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-06-05T08:03:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 11113, "name": "坦克"}, {"id": 2976, "name": "灯饰"}, {"id": 3704, "name": "鞋子"}, {"id": 11114, "name": "曲别针"}, {"id": 11115, "name": "烟灰缸"}, {"id": 11116, "name": "空气质量检测仪"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235630bpQxUCrWywLuKMAk.png", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\t<span>Curtain Light by Arik Levy </span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>Arik Levy 推出了一款“挂帘”灯饰，其设计意在把气氛性照明设备与空间分隔系统结合起来，使得不管是开灯还是关灯，这款产品都能起到自己的作用。目前有三款不同型号的灯，分别是上横梁 LED 灯具，下横档 LED 灯具，和一款上下均配备横档的 LED 灯具，三款灯可以由不同的方式排列组合，在不同场合的使用。这是 <a href=\"http://www.ariklevy.fr/\" target=\"_blank\">Arik Levy 设计工作室的官方主页</a>，点击可以查看他们更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210119O0xbPlgYeXZJCkMQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052101206OTHsWyzkrSNp9CA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210120qMejmHl8v4yCfkYN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210121f4Hm7sMzS9iRFxPD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210121qZSK2OL7BkTg0uJQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210122qV5snzyNLKHmhgeP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210122pvGrLnOkKjhJiCHl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58801956\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210122Y2JOQ6v5L8odka9c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210123EoTj7X2ekcZ0tz3b.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span>Bridal Capsule Collection by Superga &amp;  Poise Design</span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>今年运动鞋在时尚圈的有多火？总之现在连结婚都有人选择穿运动鞋了。最近，黎巴嫩女鞋品牌 Poise Design 和意大利帆布鞋品牌 Superga 联合推出了一个婚鞋系列。这个系列鞋子采用 Superga 经典白色鞋款为原型，加入施华洛世奇水晶，珍珠和蝴蝶结等浪漫的婚礼元素。其中有一款还印有 “I Do” 字样，浪漫又时尚满满。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210124wjN2oDpey7LI4xba.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210124qKa6CmRFZwHS3f5o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052101244eXbhxBLEAgOHiV6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span>Shape Based Paper Clips by Daphna Laurens </span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>荷兰设计工作室 Daphna Laurens 为 Areaware 设计了一系列几何形状曲别针。整个系列采用黑色，红色和绿色，除了普通的三角形和圆形，曲别针还有各种简单但不规则的形状。这一套曲别针是其“二维空间”系列的组成部分，也标志着 Areaware 公司整体策略的转变，即关注广阔的颜色，形状和材料，<a href=\"http://www.daphnalaurens.nl/index.php?/daphna-laurens/daphna-laurens/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看他们更多作品。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210125WNeAFKoztbJpQnTv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98288509\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210125GSdBHk58EWUwRXnF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04156479\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210126oRiyFClIAc9jGarn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63569682\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210126oE5hZQaIAbruJtLF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72738386\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210127oYuSxBJ7EsfZaFHT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.39853301\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210127K86kb7MAf0WouSDm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052101285cldiLjgmoy6AOD0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052101288clq7pZMs6TSvOK9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71393643\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tAsh Tray Skully by Christian Sjostrom\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>6 月 1 日北京禁烟令正式开始实施，不知道您怎么看待这个“史上最严禁烟令”。这是 Christian Sjostrom 设计的一个烟灰缸，“骷髅头”这个常常在禁烟宣传里面出现的意象这次出现在了他的烟灰缸中，骷髅头的“眼睛”用来弹烟灰，而“牙齿”则是倾倒烟灰的出口，黑色幽默里面包含了对“禁烟”的态度。虽然有点老套，但用来激励戒烟，或许能有一点点作用。<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/shop/design/ash-tray-skully-06-04-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210129ZTXLAmfHqhQnrOBj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210129tpxw6MnCmWAsOh43.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052101308NaOrXjoMEiH9glB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85574572\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210130rsekixj62KRmghDd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85574572\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210130U3NPabySJOkdHK9D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.85574572\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tAwair by Bitfinder\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是一款名为 “Awair” 的智能空气质量检测仪器，除了普通的空气监测，Awair 可以通过对温度，湿度，气体，颗粒等指标的分析，针对空气质量对健康的影响提出解决方案，并提出简单的建议，如开窗或饮用蜂蜜水。仪器有过敏，美容，睡眠等 6 个预设选项，选择不同的情景，Awair 都可以给出不同的解决方案。目前售价 150 美元起，<a href=\"https://getawair.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210131IkJNEaAf0GsjHWgO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.46111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210131vrtnhDV1MRLgXKU5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50925926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210132pq6zD2I7nwil9BLg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.52685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210133Hd6RnUcLrEWTCo79.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72727273\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210133LO8jxqmYtoDA7Qks.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052101349HsAcX3uq0UOnkbS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68105516\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210134k1moYPjE9XzUCBxW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t<span>EV2 by Ripsaw </span> \r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>这是把人惊呆的一个大家伙。最近，Ripsaw 推出了一款面向公众发售的军事坦克，可谓豪华震撼。不过它可不是用来打架的，这个坦克以 Ripsaw MS1 双轨机动车为原型，柴油引擎功率到达 600 马力。不仅如此，其舱内配备了丰富的娱乐设备。<a href=\"http://www.ripsawtank.com/ripsaw-ev2-media.html\" target=\"_blank\">这是 Ripsaw 官网</a>，感兴趣的话，不妨进去看看详细信息。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210135OaHESrmwqXQMFLYJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.63425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052101350eKN1a4fpRUsJl5o.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68703704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210136vCyQc2JEWjGqXshn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210136gycuvLEY0NGFpriQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210137JFlW0cNmKu1vT35j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210138PdulYb6zJ2Ws7EIr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}